2951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549970/extras/7bb36333763107a01f185ca0810c0e6d.mp4?t=1727102951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Level your character through 7 Class Kits, each with two unique abilities to use in combat and unlockable perks. Max out a variety of weapons, powering them up in stats the more you use them.</p>",
